{"tid":1032444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公投: 邊對野正Ｄ","createTime":"2019-02-22T11:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T13:44:30.000Z","uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e77a3dd121ea7ffeb769fbb6adca55ea605d83b3","tid":1032444,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:09:52.000Z","msg":"《東張西望》出過不少「有料之人」，其中林泳淘着白色背心落公園採訪手機遊戲「pokemon go」玩家，激凸身材令人印象深刻。之後網民陸續在節目中發掘出李旻芳、黃煦齡、利穎怡等人，四女更展開一場激戰，利穎怡兩度衝破重圍，包括着小背心到長洲採訪太平清醮、着吊帶牛仔裙露小蠻腰訪問五月天歌迷等等，相信有留意時事的讀者會有相當印象。<br />\n<br />\n林泳淘及利穎怡昨晚將戰場轉到港鐵車廂，林泳淘先在Ig貼出兩張合照，穿得密實的她靠在利穎怡身上嘟嘴，又留言：「我最愛的大波主持忠忠。」結果焦點當然落在利穎怡的貼身衫上。然後利穎怡反擊，貼出同一輯自拍相，不過林泳淘變成矇豬眼，又以「最愛寸我的大波主持淘淘」表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190222/large/1550805620_df9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190222%2Flarge%2F1550805620_df9e.jpg&h=55652e3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190222/large/1550805623_3e14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190222%2Flarge%2F1550805623_3e14.jpg&h=70496014&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林泳淘- <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利穎怡-<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c2ab4d73b70a690e258c00373e32cfd7e256fb","tid":1032444,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:33:46.000Z","msg":"Joker 2.0"},{"pid":"ef981fbe4e5c4d71f8b7213a21cdbff828cc5121","tid":1032444,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:35:18.000Z","msg":"留意時事???<br />\n<br />\n個記者毒撚到以為睇女=時事???"},{"pid":"9b0cd1882eeaa1ca9df52ba9e52d7f3143a4efca","tid":1032444,"uid":63842,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/F0WrZWF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF0WrZWF.png&h=8b6fef12&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}